{"word":"προσβλέπω","slug":"προσβλέπω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προσβλέπω</b></el> <el>(doric <el>ποτι-βλέπω</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-βλέψω</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ψομαι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to look at</i> or <i>upon</i>, <el>τινά</el> <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b>:—rarely <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of things, <i>to regard</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}